  Использовать :
  --------------------------------------------
    +Input-radio('gender',{options: [
    {value: 'Man1', label: 'Man1'},
    {value: 'Children1', label: 'Children1', checked: true},
    {value: 'Woman1', label: 'Woman1'},
  ]})
